thread.title: BRIEF-Hongli Zhihui Group sees FY 2017 net profit to up 149.7 pct to 175 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Hongli Zhihui Group sees FY 2017 net profit to up 149.7 pct to 175 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - hongli zhihui group co ltd

text:
Jan 24(Reuters) - Hongli Zhihui Group Co Ltd :
* Says net profit for FY 2017 to up 149.7 percent to 175 percent, or to be 345 million yuan to 380 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 138.2 million yuan
* Says increased revenue of main business as main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/T61Q6g
